        public boolean needToPrefill()
        Description copied from interface: FHIRPersistenceJDBCCache
        Returns true if the caller should attempt to prefill the caches. Prefilling must only be done before any new records are inserted to ensure the shared caches contain only data which has been previously committed to the database.
